AppCategories = Identity Management, Infrastructure
LongDescription = <div>
		The UCS Intercom Service (ICS) is a backend service that acts as an intermediary for the secure communication and Single Sign-On between other services. The ICS allows webservice backends to communicate with each other based on the Single Sign-On session of the current end user while ensuring session security.
	</div>
	<div>
		<br>
	</div>
	<div>
		The ICS is very specific for dedicated use cases, currently in the interaction between Open-Xchange, Nextcloud and elements/matrix. Details are outlined in the documentation.
		<br>
		<br>
		The App can only be installed successfully if some prerequisites are fullfilled. <b>Please consult the documentation before installation!</b>
